Floyd F. Sherman  Chief Executive Officer and Director, Builders FirstSource, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships77$4,826,387As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Floyd F. Sherman has been the Chief Executive Officer of Builders FirstSource, Inc. since 2001. Mr. Sherman served as the President of Builders FirstSource, Inc. from February 2008 to November 6, 2014. Mr. Sherman was the President of Wood Products Operations at Armstrong World Industries Inc. He served as the President of Builders FirstSource from 2001 to October 2006. Mr. Sherman served as the Chief Executive Officer of Armstrong Wood Products Inc. for nine years ... since July 1992. Prior to November 1994, he served as the President of Triangle Pacific Corp. since 1981. Prior to 1981, he served as an Executive Vice President of Triangle Pacific Corp. He worked at Triangle Pacific Corp. since 1973, for 28 years. He has been a Director of Builders FirstSource, Inc. since 2001 and PGT Innovations, Inc. since 2005. He served as a Director of C.H.I. Overhead Doors, Inc. and Armstrong Holdings, Inc. He served as the Chairman of Builders FirstSource Inc. He served as Chairman of Armstrong Wood Products, Inc. since July 1992. He served as a Director of Armstrong Wood Products Inc., since 1982. Mr. Sherman is a veteran of the U.S. Army. He is a graduate of the New York State College of Forestry at Syracuse University and holds an MBA degree from Georgia State University.Read Full Background




