Insider Activity


Individual




Floyd F. Sherman



Mr. Floyd F. Sherman is on the Board of Directors at PGT Innovations, Inc., Builders FirstSource, Inc. and C.H.I. Overhead Doors, Inc. Mr. Sherman was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Armstrong Floor Products and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Triangle Pacific Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from SUNY College of Environmental Science and an MBA from Georgia State University.



